'''Laura Cappato''' (born [[October 13]], [[1960s|1967]] in [[Wikipedia:Venice|Venice]], [[Wikipedia:Italy|Italy]]) worked as the production coordinator in Italy for both [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]. Other notable works include both of the [[Wikipedia:The Omega Code|Omega Code]] movies.

